OL,3,C'Arrogant' driver caused crash which
OL,4,Ckilled three teenage friends instantly
OL,6,FRachel Bullock was at Teesside Crown
OL,7,FCourt for the sentencing of Joshua
OL,8,FChapman
OL,10,FA 20-year-old man whose three teenage
OL,11,Ffriends were killed instantly when his
OL,12,Fcar crashed into a tree in North
OL,13,FYorkshire has been jailed.
OL,15,FJoshua Chapman drove his Alfa Romeo at
OL,16,F"grossly excessive" speeds on a dark
OL,17,Fstretch of a country road near Bedale
OL,18,Fin July 2022 before crashing into the
OL,19,Ftree, a court has heard.
