OL,3,C'Arrogant' driver caused crash which
OL,4,Ckilled three teenage friends instantly
OL,6,FAt Teesside Crown Court on Thursday
OL,7,F(14 March), Chapman, of Mosquito
OL,8,FCourt, Bedale, was sentenced to nine
OL,9,Fyears and four months behind bars and
OL,10,Fwas banned from driving for ten years.
OL,12,FJudge Jonathan Carroll condemned
OL,13,FChapman's actions, describing how his
OL,14,F"harm to these families could hardly
OL,15,Fhave been greater" ` "robbing them of
OL,16,Ftheir much loved boys, and taking the
OL,17,Flives of three highly promising young
OL,18,Fmen".
