OL,3,C'Arrogant' driver caused crash which
OL,4,Ckilled three teenage friends instantly
OL,6,FThe court was told Chapman was 18 and
OL,7,Fhad passed his test only ten months
OL,8,Fbefore the evening of the crash in
OL,9,Fwhich his three friends died.
OL,11,FLate on the night of 29 July 2022,
OL,12,FLouis Banks, 17, and 18-year-olds
OL,13,FTommy Shevels and Aaron Bell got into
OL,14,FChapman's Alpha Romeo to go to a
OL,15,Fnearby McDonalds, the court heard.
OL,17,FThere, Chapman was caught on CCTV
OL,18,Fspeeding around the car park before
OL,19,Fheading out onto the twisting B6268
OL,20,FBedale to Masham road.
