OL,3,C'Arrogant' driver caused crash which
OL,4,Ckilled three teenage friends instantly
OL,6,FOne of the passengers, Aaron, texted a
OL,7,Ffriend from inside the car which read:
OL,8,F"Oh my God, please save me."
OL,10,FMoments later, Chapman had sped
OL,11,Fthrough a red roadworks light, turning
OL,12,Fa sharp bend at 75mph and lost
OL,13,Fcontrol, hitting a tree.
OL,15,FAll three of the victims' mothers were
OL,16,Fin court and made emotional statements
OL,17,Fabout the impact the loss of their
OL,18,Fchildren had on them.
