OL,3,C'Arrogant' driver caused crash which
OL,4,Ckilled three teenage friends instantly
OL,6,FThey told Chapman that his "arrogant",
OL,7,F"selfish", "showing off" had
OL,8,Fdevastated their families and their
OL,9,Flives.
OL,11,FNicola Percy described her son Aaron
OL,12,Fas "my son, my world and my best
OL,13,Fbuddy".
OL,15,FMrs Percy told the court that she had
OL,16,Fbeen "horrified" to discover that
OL,17,FChapman had set up a TikTok account
OL,18,Fexplaining how to make cars,
OL,19,Fparticularly Alfa Romeos, go faster.
