OL,6,F"There are no words," she said, and
OL,7,Fturning to Chapman who was in the dock
OL,8,Fshe added: "There are days when I
OL,9,Fdon't want to get out of bed."
OL,11,FThe mothers of the two other boys `
OL,12,FTommy and Louis ` spoke of how their
OL,13,F"indescribable grief walks beside them
OL,14,Feveryday" and how their "beautiful
OL,15,Fboys have had such promising lives
OL,16,Fsnatched from them".
OL,18,FChapman pleaded guilty to three counts
OL,19,Fof causing death by dangerous driving
OL,20,Fat a previous hearing.
