OL,6,FIn mitigation, Chapman's barrister
OL,7,FJazmine Lee said the now 20-year-old
OL,8,Ffelt "colossal guilt" and has had
OL,9,Fsuicidal thoughts.
OL,11,FDisqualifying him from driving for 10
OL,12,Fyears ` and jailing him for 9 years 4
OL,13,Fmonths - Judge Carroll told Chapman he
OL,14,Fhad caused "a catastrophic loss for
OL,15,Fthree families" - "families who are
OL,16,Fleft with holes that can never be
OL,17,Ffilled".
